2100:Her eyes opened.\p;
2200:And then, she looked at me.\p;
2300:Could this Rimi have been the one I knew? <i>T</i><i>h</i><i>a</i><i>t</i> Rimi?\n;Or was it an entirely different one?\p;
2400:I didn't know.\n;I was afraid to call her name.\n;So I waited for her to say something.\p;
