3100:I buried my face in her chest.\n;The feeling of her soft, supple breasts spread across my cheeks.\p;
3200:Gravity soon disappeared.\n;And the two of us began drifting along the blue.\p;
3300:〔Rimi〕“I heard your voice, Taku.”\p;
3400:〔Rimi〕“‘Wake up, Rimi!’ you cried out to me.”\p;
3500:〔Takumi〕“Thank goodness... *sniffle*... Thank goodness...”\p;
3600:With her still lying on the ground, Rimi held me as she gently stroked my hair.\p;
3700:I couldn't describe how wonderful that felt. It was as if the very essence of all her kindness and warmth was enveloping me.\n;It reminded me of how I felt when my mom hugged me back when I was a kid—how safe I'd felt in her arms.\p;
3800:I wanted to stay like this forever, but at the same time, I wanted to confirm for myself that she really was Rimi, so I turned my head just enough to look at her face.\p;
