7100:〔Rimi〕“So, this time, I'll be the one who protects you two.”\p;
7200:I still didn't understand what she meant by “Taku” and “Takumi,” but what I did know was that if she was there to protect me, I wouldn't need to worry about anything anymore. She was a Gigalomaniac, and she would keep me safe.\p;
