7600:Atoning for her sins... Was she talking about what she'd done to Sena and Kozupii? But that had been legitimate self-defense. She hadn't had a choice, and that should've been how she thought about it.\p;
7700:But what felt far more strange to me... was how she'd said “you both.”\n;Who else did she mean?\p;
